name: Good Vibes - Music #1 of 27
description:
Waking up late in a city full of sin,
Hang Over kicking in, Fvck work I'm calling in,
Boss is giving me shit, It's the second time this week,
He's all about the cheddar, I'm more about the cheese,
And the way that I see it, It's the root of all evil,
If all of us had it, We would be all equal,
But since we're on the subject, Yes, I'm balling on a budget,
Sitting in lower class and I'm getting right above it,
That's the goal and I'll hunt it, Won't stop until it happens,
I try to stay focused, but I always get distracted,
Smoking weed, less active, less work, more laughing,
Never carried heat unless it's cigarettes I'm packing,
Time is never stopping and life is too precious,
The man up above put us here just to test us,
Doing bad things only with good intentions,
He'll forgive you in the end,
I just thought that I should mention it.

Life's too short, but it's okay, we'll keep on living through another day,
With good vibes, good vibes, good vibes and good vibes - X2

Can you feel the heat, it's the middle of the summer,
Lakers lost again and I know it's a bummer..
But life goes on and it's alright,
We're gonna party like the world is ending tonight and that's right..
Just live it how you live it,
And don't ever let someone ever tell you different,
This is your story and you're written in the pages,
Keep doing great things and live on through the ages,
Get a golden chance? Might as well take it,
You only live once, so who knows if you will make it,
Falling while your standing or hit a crash landing?
Get up like a champ and they will keep on chanting,
Like a King or a Queen no matter who you are,
Live life to the fullest and shine with the stars,
24/7, Winter, spring, summer, fall,
Live life to the fullest and shine with the stars.

Life's too short, but it's okay, we'll keep on living through another day,
With good vibes, good vibes, good vibes and good vibes - X2
